The list of ideas for the project.
1. Create as system which is portable.
2. The Bus Reservation system will have 2 main options [1st Administrative Access, 2nd Customer Portal].
3. The Administrative Access should contain the following:
    a. A login option for security.
    b. Ability to insert/delete bus details.
    c. Check Reservation.
4. The Customer Portal should contain the following:
    a. Option to Show all buses.
    b. Option to Show bus details.
    c. Option to make Reservation.
5. An exit button should be present to return to home.
